data.description: Lots of space and a great price! Open concept living, gorgeous kitchen, covered back patio! Downstairs master and rest bedrooms up with living and game area.  Main living with decorative brick fireplace which leads into formal dining room allowing for those large gatherings without being cramped for space.  Updated eat in kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and island, updated backsplash, and large pantry.  Perfect central space to gather with easy access to covered back patio and large flat, trampoline sized yard. Note a half bath downstairs also! The downstairs owner's suite includes granite vanity with dual square sinks, decorative lighting, walk in closet with new flooring, garden tub & separate shower.  Upstairs large landing along with three additional bedrooms, full bath and large game  living space with new, big fun ceiling fan.    Community has a pool, sport court and playground.  Motivated.
